The _Qatar Visitor_ blog reports today: “The Qatar Supreme Desert Development
Council is planning its most ambitious project yet – a snow city to be located
in the heart of the [Qatar
Desert](http://qatarvisitor.blogspot.com/2009/04/qatar-snow-city.html)…as the
snow will be generated via solar-nuclear energy the project will actually run
best in the searing heat of the summer.”

